SkyeCDE Hub Directive

Core role

SkyeCDE is not a stub anymore.
SkyeCDE is the hub platform for the new IDE builds.
Every upgraded IDE build should live under SkyeCDE so users can switch between them from one platform.

Hub root
- /workspaces/SkyeCDE/Skye0s-s0l26/Sky0s-Platforms/SkyeCDE

Hub responsibilities
- hold the upgraded IDE builds
- provide a central launch hub for every new IDE
- keep the original products separate and intact
- let users swap between upgraded IDE builds without leaving the SkyeCDE platform
- act as the parent platform for future CDE-class builds

